snippet.textDisplay:
If the United States, Italy, Spain, and other countries with the highest number of confirmed COVID-19 cases follow the pattern reported by China and will soon begin to level off in both the number of new cases and number of deaths, then we will know China has been at least reasonably truthful in its reporting of the COVID-19 pandemic. If, however, the number of new cases and deaths continue to rise at the extremely steep, near exponential, rates they are currently rising, then we can be certain China has been and likely is continuing to lie and lie massively to the world about the scale of the pandemic within its own borders.
Perhaps one benefit, if there can be any, to the COVID-19 pandemic could be to demonstrate absolutely and undeniably to the entire world China's level of credibility.

snippet.textDisplay:
As a Chinese, I just want to tell ordinary citizens in Europe and the United States, no matter the source of politics and virus, now is the time to help themselves!

First of all, I am a medical student. In addition to my previous experience, this infectious disease has an average incubation period of 14 days. There is no symptom in the incubation period, but it is infectious. The transmission way is air transmission. It is necessary to wear a mask for aerosol transmission (the virus is in saliva and has a long survival time). In addition, the virus is also found in the urine and feces of the infected person Common contact transmission, disinfectant and 75% alcohol can eliminate it, but do not drink alcohol, because it is harmful to the body, and can not eliminate the virus deep in the lungs, and pay attention not to spray alcohol in the closed environment, because when encountering open fire, it will burn quickly, you should know that although the virus is deadly, it will die faster! Solve this problem as long as the ventilation after disinfection!
So, in addition to these, what else should we pay attention to?

1. Express delivery: after the hand washing, wipe the inside with disinfectant!
2. Meat: it must be cooked!
3. Take out: try not to order!
4. Packing bag: it can't be sterilized and flushed with hot water!
5. Going out: a. the elderly and children should not go out as much as possible B. pay attention to the handle outside the house, the elevator button, and wear disposable gloves. If not, remember to disinfect the hand after touching it c. girls go out and tie their hair. Boys and girls should wear hats to prevent their hair from contacting bacteria D. after going home, change clothes, wash hands, disinfect shoes, and wipe the mobile phone with disinfectant
6. Pets: for example, keep more cat food and cat litter to prevent out of stock
7. What can be done: A. less going out, no pick-up B. reasonable diet, increased resistance C. more clothes, no cold and fever, no cold to prevent coughing D. pay attention to the epidemic situation but don't believe in rumors and don't spread rumors E Take the temperature of your family every day. If the temperature is above 37.3 ℃, you will have a fever. Do not take any antipyretics. Generally, a fever will be cured in one or two days, but if you are really ill, do not delay your illness, actively report the active treatment, and be responsible for everyone

In addition, there is no discomfort, do not rush to test, which will increase the chance of infection
作为中国人，我只想告诉普通欧美普通的市民，不管政治和病毒的源头，现在是需要自救的时候！
首先，我是学医的，再加上前段时间的经验，这个传染病它有一个平均十四天的潜伏期，潜伏期没有症状，但是有传染性，传播途径有空气传播，气溶胶传播（病毒在唾液里，存活时间较长）所以戴口罩很有必要，而且在感染者的尿液和粪便中也发现了病毒，还有常见的接触传播，消毒液和75%的酒精能消灭它，但是不要喝酒精，因为对身体有伤害，还消灭不了肺部深处的病毒，而且注意不要在密闭的环境喷洒酒精，因为遇到明火会快速燃烧，你要知道，虽然病毒致命，但这样会死得更快！解决这个问题只要消毒后通风就好！
那么，除了这些，还需要注意什么呢？
1.快递：拆完洗手，里面的用消毒液擦拭！
2.肉类：一定要煮熟！
3.外卖：尽量不点！
4.包装袋：不能消毒的用热水冲冲！
5.出门：a.老人小孩尽量不要出门 b.注意家门外的把手，电梯按钮，戴一次性手套，没有的话，摸完记得消毒手 c.女生出门扎头发，男女生最好戴帽子，防止头发接触细菌d.回家后衣物换洗，洗手，消毒鞋子，消毒液擦拭手机
6.宠物：比如养猫多备些猫粮猫砂，防止断货
7.可以做的事：a.少出门，不接客 b.合理饮食，增加抵抗力 c.多穿衣物不让自己感冒发烧，不吃凉的防止咳嗽d.关注疫情但不信谣不传谣 e. 每天给家人测体温，37.3℃以上属于发烧，不要吃退烧药，因为一般发烧一两天会好，但是真的得病了不要耽误病情，积极汇报积极治疗，对所有人负责
另外，没有不适，不要抢着去检测，这样会增加传染机会
